Class TransactionHistoryParams

java.lang.Object
com.binance4j.core.param.Params

com.binance4j.core.param.IntervalParams
com.binance4j.nft.param.TransactionHistoryParams
public class TransactionHistoryParams extends com.binance4j.core.param.IntervalParams
A NFT transaction history request

The max interval between startTime and endTime is 90 days.

If startTime and endTime are not sent, the recent 7 days' data will be returned.
